  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/ba582390f9a4e6403b57ed76d7d72851.avif?t=1772537506\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/c38964481b07e23cb30c015dfc9a8b47.poster.avif?t=1772537506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/c38964481b07e23cb30c015dfc9a8b47.webm?t=1772537506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/c38964481b07e23cb30c015dfc9a8b47.mp4?t=1772537506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conquer Mars, fend off alien threats, and secure your path to survival!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on dangerous expeditions to gather intel and resources. Fight off hordes of alien creatures and save other survivors. Use their skills and knowledge to defend your base from a huge enemy attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/c098e5086e71bae220d38f12cba6ac6b.avif?t=1772537506\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/934dc58c4083b3f9944a2e400d58a9d8.poster.avif?t=1772537506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/934dc58c4083b3f9944a2e400d58a9d8.webm?t=1772537506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385380/extras/934dc58c4083b3f9944a2e400d58a9d8.mp4?t=1772537506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate Mars's challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the planet's secrets and discover hidden materials </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a shelter and protect yourself from the harsh Martian environment!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend against alien invasions and uncover secrets of the creatures of Mars!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather oxygen and essential materials from old rocket ships to survive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize your escape mission and secure your passage back to Earth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open epic loot boxes to swap or upgrade your gear</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the last man standing on Mars, navigate through the wilderness, and prove your survival skills!</p>",
